defaultOAR0018defaultWritten evidence submitted by the LGAdefault&#xa0;defaultIntroductiondefault&#xa0;defaultThe Local Government Association (LGA) is the national voice of local government.  We work with councils to support, promote and 
defaultimprove local government.
default&#xa0;
defaultWe are a politically-led, cross party organisation which works on behalf of councils to ensure local government has a strong, credible voice with national government.  We aim to influence and set the political agenda on the issue
defaults that matter to councils so they are able to deliver local solutions to national problems.
default  
default&#xa0;
defaultThe LGA covers every part of England and Wales, supporting local government as the most efficient and accountable part of the public sector.
